Bobertron not knowing if his plan to join Megatron would work. He left Magmatron's base for better things. He walked across the plant trying to think of how to convince Megs he was a great help to him. He decided that he would just wait for a reply. He sent a mess to megs " Megatron if you pleases, please respond to my mess even if it is a no. My future depends on you. Despare is an emotion you can trust as you say."
